creator: webWise Network Consultants Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Supercharge your mobile staff with Form Sumo. No more paper and clipboards! Design your own forms and inspections to be used by your mobile teams out in the field. Publish lists like corporate phone directories or standard documents.

Our cloud service allows you to create your own customised forms using simple drag and drop. Once the form is created, your team members will see the new form available on their device. The completed forms can be emailed (pdf or html format) or sent automatically to your corporate back office system for automated processing.

Typical uses are:
- Site safety audits
- Behavioural based observations
- Plant / machinery prestart checks
- Real estate rental property inspections
- Timesheets

Imagine:
- Completing a prestart on your equipment and have your maintenance department instantly notified of any defects and machine hours for the next service interval
- Perform a property inspection complete with photos

Rich form controls allow:
- text
- date and time
- geolocation
- signatures
- multi-select lists
- radio buttons
- single-select lists
- toggles (yes/no)
- photos
...and much more

Form Sumo works while you are internet connected or offline, with completed forms stored and submitting once internet connectivity is available.

A comprehensive and simple web API allows easy connection to your corporate data.
descriptionShort: Complete custom forms on your mobile device. No more paper!
